{"tid":2298431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国公路40多輛車連環撞大車禍 10多輛車起火  甲醇運載車大爆炸","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T13:19:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8390b7e9fae9bcfb2b776543a0449d77290bc569","tid":2298431,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"大陸中央電視台報導，陝西「包茂高速公路」在「關莊溝大橋」路段，今天（24號）早上7點，發生40多輛車相撞的嚴重交通事故。相撞的40多輛車中，其中有一輛是34噸的甲醇運載車，這輛車中的甲醇起火，波及其他10多輛車，有多人被困，陝西方面已經派警消人員前往救援。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，當地消防救援指揮中心獲報後，立即調派特勤人員前往支援救災，警消人員幾乎全員出動。<br />\n<br />\n這起大車禍在早上7點發生後，7點29分，特勤救援人員已經到達現場，展開救援，現場持續救援中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bcc.com.tw/onair/ysy_20201124_114300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcc.com.tw%2Fonair%2Fysy_20201124_114300.jpg&h=e861050c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bcc.com.tw/newsView.4839771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcc.com.tw%2FnewsView.4839771&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=ec5ee616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bcc.com.tw/newsView.4839771</a>"},{"pid":"a92a17801591b250be8e2db7ee72f964d18445fa","tid":2298431,"uid":63909,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"有GIF 未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c123eb31bd1531ce51e5f0116b7b24b08e0d0f","tid":2298431,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e6fe84